'''假寡婦蜘蛛'''（学名：{{lang|la|Steatoda nobilis}}，{{lang-en|False Widow Spider}}），[[姬蛛科|姬蛛科]]，[[鳴姬蛛屬|鳴姬蛛屬]]，假寡婦種。是形似[[黑寡婦蜘蛛|黑寡婦蜘蛛]]的蜘蛛。擁有劇毒，是英國十二種咬人蜘蛛中最毒的。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ettoday.net/news/20131024/286377.htm |title=毒蜘蛛「假寡婦」咬一口休養一年　英國中學急關閉消毒-東森新聞雲 |accessdate=2020-10-12 |archive-date=2015-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006182546/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20131024/286377.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science/2014/09/140930_uk_spider_finger |title=英女子被假黑寡婦蜘蛛咬後截去手指-BBC中文網 |accessdate=2020-10-12 |archive-date=2015-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150903234144/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science/2014/09/140930_uk_spider_finger |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[https://news.ebc.net.tw/news/world/177594 假寡婦咬5次！26歲爸爆痛紅腫…心靈受創傷-東森新聞]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2910918 |title=遭毒蛛「假寡婦」夜襲5次 26歲男子傷口潰爛臥床2個月-自由電子報 |accessdate=2020-10-12 |archive-date=2019-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191004072644/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2910918 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20150913003082-260408?chdtv 英國寒冬將至 專家警告小心「假寡婦」敲門-中時新聞網]</ref>在英國被稱作高貴的假寡婦。原產於[[馬德拉|馬德拉]]和[[加那利群島|加那利群島]]。也被發現在[[加州|加州]]和[[智利|智利]]。約1879年隨著貨物運至[[托基|托基]]。<ref>[Octavius Pickard-Cambridge (1879). "On some new and rare British spiders, with characters of a new genus"]</ref>

==症狀==
蜘蛛的毒液會引起發炎紅腫，潰爛。根據[[英國太陽報|英國太陽報]]報導，一名婦人因不小心弄壞了蜘蛛網，結果遭到假寡婦攻擊，回到家不以為意，消毒清潔流血的傷口。隔天感覺到腿像是有人充氣，像石頭一樣。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.thesun.co.uk/news/12786950/false-widow-spider-sex-crazed-frenzy-bites-gran/ |title=False widow spider in ‘sex-crazed frenzy’ due to mating season bites gran making her leg blow up like ‘massive balloon’-the sun |accessdate=2020-10-12 |archive-date=2020-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119212922/https://www.thesun.co.uk/news/12786950/false-widow-spider-sex-crazed-frenzy-bites-gran/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==特徵==
雌性體型從 9.5 到 14 毫米（mm）不等，而雄性則是 7 到 11 毫米。[1]最大的雌性為 13.7 毫米，而最大的雄性為 11.66 毫米。有別一般蜘蛛，他們在夏天繁殖期時，特別會主動攻擊人。一般傷口不大，但不積極治療後果併發[[蜂窩性組織炎|蜂窩性組織炎]]，甚至可能[[截肢|截肢]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20150918/XBI34YA73KCVHKKMBTZTWVR63Y/ |title=香港蘋果日報-假寡婦蛛咬一口 得意妹爛腳無得走 |access-date=2020-10-13 |archive-date=2021-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210621165403/https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20150918/XBI34YA73KCVHKKMBTZTWVR63Y/ }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/629663 |title=自由電子報-「假寡婦」咬一口 英國婦女險截肢 |accessdate=2020-10-13 |archive-date=2020-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201014143551/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/629663 |dead-url=no }}</ref>根據[[每日郵報|每日郵報]]報導，一名七歲女童被其咬傷，當地醫務人員並沒察覺是假寡婦所致，後來傷口擴大，轉至魯姆菲爾德醫院，一位醫生看了並了解到是假寡婦咬傷的。因為他之前也被咬過。<ref>[https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6127661/ Daily Mail online-Seven-year-old girl girl's skin is being EATEN AWAY after she was bitten by a false widow spider on a sleepover and is now on hospital IV drip]</ref>

==危險==
英國[[自然史博物館_(倫敦)|自然史博物館]]表示有六種常住英國。其中有三種假寡婦最常見。
*兔食蜘蛛（Steatoda bipunctata）
*櫥櫃蜘蛛（Steatoda grossa）
*高貴的假寡婦（Steatoda nobilis）
在英國有近650種蜘蛛。而會咬人的僅不到一成。<ref>{{cite web |author1=The Trustees of The Natural History Museum, London |title=How dangerous are false widow spiders? |url=https://www.nhm.ac.uk/discover/how-dangerous-are-false-widow-spiders.html |website=www.nhm.ac.uk |publisher=The Trustees of The Natural History Museum, London |accessdate=2020-10-26 |archive-date=2020-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207185250/https://www.nhm.ac.uk/discover/how-dangerous-are-false-widow-spiders.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

